                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.8">
                        <locus from="44r" to="57v" facs="044"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3082RepCh362">Malkǝʾa kidāna mǝḥrat</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">እግዚአብሔር፡ ወሀቤ፡ ብርሃን፡ ዘይሤልሰ፡ በአካሉ። እንዘ፡ ተዋህዶ፡ ያጸንዕ፡ በመለኮቱ፡ ወኃይሉ።</incipit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.9">
                        <locus from="57v" to="60v" facs="058"/>
                        <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1295Dersan#Sälam">Dǝrsāna Mikāʾel,  Sälam</title>
                        <note>copied for <foreign xml:lang="gez">አቅባ፡ ሚካኤል፡</foreign> <locus target="#60v" facs="061"/></note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.10">
                        <locus from="61v" to="75v" facs="062"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2835RepCh119">Malkǝʾa Mikāʾel</title>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.11">
                        <locus from="76r" to="80r" facs="076"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2908RepCh189">Malkǝʾa Śǝllāse</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምክሙ፡ ዘእምቅድመ፡ ዓለም፡ ህልው። ለር፤እስክሙ፡ ሰላም፡ ወስእርትክሙ፡ ፅእድው።</incipit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.12">
                        <locus from="80r" to="91v" facs="080"/>
                        <title>Image of Mäzra'tä Krǝstos, <foreign xml:lang="gez">መልክዐ፡ መዝራዕተ፡ ክርስቶስ፡</foreign></title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">ይትባረክ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘአምጽአ፡ ዓለማተ። መዝራዕተ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ያሬድ፡ እንዘ፡ ትብል፡ ክሡተ። ኢያዕረፍከ፡ እምተናግሮ፡ ወኢረሰይከ፡ ሀኬተ።</incipit>
                        <note>Concluded with a litany for the Nativity, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ምልጣነ፤ ተወልደ፡ እምድንግል። ሰከበ፡ ውስተ፡ ጎል።</foreign><locus target="#91r #91v" facs="091 092"/></note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.13">
                        <locus from="92r" to="94v" facs="092"/>
                        <title>List of the sufferings of Jesus</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">ጸዋትወ፡ ሕማማት፡ ዘእግዚእነ፡ ወመድኀኒነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ዘዘበጥዎ፡ ገጾ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                </incipit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.14">
                        <locus from="94v" to="95r" facs="095"/>
                        <title>Sälam to Täklä Haymanot, taken from <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1325egziab">ʾƎgziʾabǝḥer nagśa (General record)</title></title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ናሕርየ፡ ወንጌል፡ ወወኦሪት። እምአመ፡ ተወልደ፡ ሰአት። ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ባረኮ፡ በሰላስ፡ ዕለት።</incipit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.15">
                        <locus from="95v" to="95r" facs="096"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2851RepCh133">Malkəʾa Kiros</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምከ፡ ኀበ፡ ዓምደ፡ ወርቅ፡ ዘተጽሕገ። ምስለ፡ አበው፡ ኄራን፡ እንዘ፡ ይከውን፡ ሱቱፈ።</incipit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.16">
                        <locus from="95v" to="102r" facs="096"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2930RepCh211">Malkǝʾa ʾAbuna Takla Hāymānot</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለጽንሰትከ፡ ወለልደትከ፡ እምከርሥ። አመ፡ ፳ወረቡዑ፡ ለወርኃ፡ ታኅሣሥ።</incipit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.17">
                        <locus from="104r" to="126v" facs="104"/>
                        <title>Image of the Trinity, <foreign xml:lang="gez">መልክዐ፡ ሥላሴ፡</foreign></title>
                        <note>Composed probably by a certain <foreign xml:lang="gez">ታቦር፡</foreign> after <foreign xml:lang="gez">ኢያሱ፡</foreign> (1682–1706) built the <foreign xml:lang="gez">ደብረ፡ ብርሃነ፡ ሥላሴ፡</foreign> church in Gondär, cf. <locus target="#127r #129r" facs="127 129"/></note>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለሕጽንክሙ፡ ምርፋቀ፡ ጻድቃን፡ አግብርቲሁ። ማያተ፡ ኢያሱ፡ ሥላሴ፡ እለ፡ ትውሕዙ፡ እምሕሊናሁ።</incipit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.18">
                        <locus from="127r" to="129r" facs="127"/>
                        <title>Sälam, to <foreign xml:lang="gez">አቡነፍር፡</foreign>, of <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሰኔ፡ ፲፮፡</foreign></title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">ስላም፡ ለአቡናር፡ ጊዜ፡ ተዳደቆ፡ መዊጥ። እንተ፡ ተወለጠ፡ ግጹ፡ አምሳለ፡ እሳጥ።</incipit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.19">
                        <locus from="129r" facs="129"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer">Asmat prayer against rinderpest (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ኅኮር፡ (?)</foreign>)</title>
                        <note> The Greek names of the nails of the cross are copied on <locus target="#130v" facs="131"/></note>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">አስማት፡ በእንተ፡ እንስሳ፡ ወበእንተ፡ አባግዕ፡ ወበእንተ፡ አጣሌ፡ ወኵሉ፡ ንዋየ፡ ሰብእ፡ ከመ፡ ኢይንድፋ፡  ለዓራዊት፡ ኅኮር፡ በኀጸ፡ ቀጢን፡<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.20">
                        <locus from="129v" to="131r" facs="130"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2765RepCh49">Malkǝʾ-hymn (Salām) to Phanuel</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለከ፡ ሰዳዴ፡ ሰዳዴ፡ አጋንንት፡ ፋኑኤል፡ ለእግዚብሔር፡ እምጽርሑ። ከመ፡ ኢይስክዩ፡ ሰብአ፡ እነ፡ ኢነስሑ።</incipit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.21">
                        <locus from="134v" to="138r" facs="135"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1190Baenta">Baʾǝnta qǝddǝsāt</title>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.22">
                        <locus from="138v" to="140r" facs="139"/>
                        <title>What seems to be a hymn/song praising what <foreign xml:lang="gez">ኢዮአስ፡</foreign> (1747–1761) has done for the monastery of Abunä Täklä Haymanot</title>
                        <notatedMusic>
                          <desc>Supplied with musical notation, insufficiently legible</desc>
                        </notatedMusic>
                     </msItem>
                  </msItem>

